description: Deletes tags from an Application Auto Scaling scalable target. To delete a tag, specify the tag key and the Application Auto Scaling scalable target.

parameters.name: ResourceARN
parameters.description: Identifies the Application Auto Scaling scalable target from which to remove tags. For example: arn:aws:application-autoscaling:us-east-1:123456789012:scalable-target/1234abcd56ab78cd901ef1234567890ab123 To get the ARN for a scalable target, use  DescribeScalableTargets.

parameters.name: TagKeys
parameters.description: One or more tag keys. Specify only the tag keys, not the tag values. (string) ---
